#

Creamy Bacon and Egg Carbonara

25 min
$7.5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

EggsDairy

Dietary Tags:

QuickComfort Food

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

PastaItalianEasyComfort Food

Description

A rich and creamy pasta dish with crispy bacon and a silky egg sauce that comes together in no time!

Ingredients

  • spaghetti: 200g
  • bacon: 150g
  • eggs: 2 large
  • parmesan cheese: 50g
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • black pepper: to taste
  • salt: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
